            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "78:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَكَوَاعِبَ﴾: نَوَاهِدَ، أَثْدَاؤُهنَّ مُرْتَفِعَةٌ لم تَتَدَلَّ.</p>\n<h2>﴿أَتۡرَابٗا﴾: مُسْتَوِياتٍ في سِنٍّ واحِدةٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "78:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿دِهَاقٗا﴾: مَمْلُوءةً خَمْراً.</h2>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
                "78:35": {
                    "id": 35
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لَا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا﴾: باطِلاً مِنَ القول.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَلَا كِذَّٰبٗا﴾: ولا تَكْذِيباً.</h2>"
        },
        "36": {
            "verses": {
                "78:36": {
                    "id": 36
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿حِسَابٗا﴾: كَثِيراً كافياً لَهُم.</h2>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "78:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
